  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Zefer Tyranus, a quiet House Ko'iron curator in the Spire of Hive Primus, finds a clue to an artefact that may tie his House to Necromunda's founders. The trail pulls him downward into the Underhive, where a spy, a charismatic Redemption-flavoured gang leader and a librarian with her own designs all chase the same relic. Spire politics and hive-bottom danger rub against stranger hints of buried history, with faith, class and old technology making each level feel more hostile than the last. A sombre vertical-descent mystery, part court intrigue and part undercity quest.",
